snippet.title: DiRT 4 — Coming to macOS and Linux
snippet.description:
Get behind the wheel of the most powerful machines ever made as you face the world’s toughest environments and circuits in rally, rallycross, and landrush races.

DiRT 4 is on track for macOS and Linux in 2019
